title: Angel Soft Toilet Paper, 12 Jumbo Rolls

description.detailed:
• Angel Soft toilet paper is designed with softness and strength at a price that won?t break the bank. Roll for roll, Angel Soft gives you the quality you expect at a value you?ll love.
  • Get softness and strength all rolled into one with Angel Soft toilet paper. Our 2-ply toilet paper rolls also deliver on value, so you can save your hard-earned money without having to give up the quality and comfort you love about Angel Soft toilet paper.
  • Sustainable Forestry Initiative (SFI) certified Angel Soft toilet paper is made with sustainably-sourced trees.
  • The full line of Angel Soft toilet paper is septic-safe for well-maintained sewer and septic systems. Angel Soft toilet paper packaging is recyclable. The plastic wrapper has a resin identification number of 4. Please check with your local recycling facility to determine if these materials are recycled in your area.
  • Angel Soft rolls fit standard bathroom toilet paper holders.

  • Pack contains 9 Rolls (286 sheets per roll) of Charmin Ultra Strong Toilet Paper
  • 1 Charmin Mega Roll = 4 Regular Rolls based on number of sheets in Charmin Regular Roll bath tissue
  • Design inspired by washcloth-like cleaning
  • Strong 2-ply toilet paper to help clean better
  • 4X stronger when wet vs. the leading bargain brand
  • Clog-safe, septic-safe and Roto-Rooter approved
  • We all go to the bathroom, those who go with Charmin Ultra Strong toilet paper really Enjoy the Go!
  • At Charmin, we are committed to making our toilet paper work hard to make a sustainable difference. 100% of our paper comes from responsibly managed forests
